item.title: By: Tilwen
item.dc:creator: Tilwen
item.description: HI ! Interesting game, because white plays really strangely, but not that bad. This kind of player make you have to try and discover some new things, and understand other mechanisms about go. Anyway, I have one remark about your commentary, one move you don't discuss at all, and which seems big to me. The move 63 is bad shape in my opinion, I would propose the other nobi (the point white just takes after this, which gives him good (eye) shape), this one threats to cut and makes yourself connect.
